('1ef936c1-a034-4778-bb47-f3b95c439071', '9244b6b0-c51a-4fc2-a363-1c7d9b2fa5dc', 'approved', '2022-04-19', 'Matt told her to reach for the stars, but Veronica thought it was the most ridiculous advice she''d ever received.', 'Free masks and hand sanitizer'),
